OL,7,FThe Chair of the Police Federation for
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland, Liam Kelly, has hit
OL,9,Fout at the decision to second a senior
OL,10,FPSNI officer who .
OL,12,FMr Kelly has called for a thorough
OL,13,Fexamination of the processes that
OL,14,Fallowed the Policing Board to
OL,15,Frecommend the secondment of Deputy
OL,16,FChief Constable Mark Hamilton.
