OL,7,FIn September last year the Police
OL,8,FFederation which represents rank-and-
OL,9,Ffile officers passed a vote of no
OL,10,Fconfidence over Hamilton's handling of
OL,11,Fthe high-profile Ormeau Road
OL,12,Fcommemoration incident that led to two
OL,13,Fofficers being disciplined.
OL,15,FA High Court judge ruled that the
OL,16,Fdisciplinary process against the two
OL,17,Fjunior officers had been unlawful.
