OL,7,FThe court ruling was one of a series
OL,8,Fof controversies within the PSNI that
OL,9,Fled to the resignation of Chief
OL,10,FConstable Simon Byrne. Jon Boutcher
OL,11,Fwent on to replace Mr Byrne as the
OL,12,Fregion's top-ranking officer.
OL,14,FMark Hamilton has been away from work
OL,15,Fsince September 2023 after undergoing .
OL,17,FHe is now set to spend the remainder
OL,18,Fof 2024 on a secondment that will
OL,19,Finvolve work with the Department of
OL,20,FJustice and the National Police
OL,21,FChiefs' Council.
