OL,7,FThose two employers will part fund Mr
OL,8,FHamilton's salary during the 10-month
OL,9,Fsecondment period.
OL,11,FA spokeswoman for the Northern Ireland
OL,12,FPolicing Board, the PSNI's oversight
OL,13,Fbody, confirmed the secondment plan.
OL,15,FShe said it was now subject to
OL,16,Fapproval by Justice Minister Naomi
OL,17,FLong.
