OL,7,FMr Kelly said the Policing Board's
OL,8,Fdecision reinforces the view amongst
OL,9,Frank-and-file officers that senior
OL,10,Fofficers are treated totally
OL,11,Fdifferently from their junior
OL,12,Fcolleagues.
