OL,7,FMr Kelly said: "The officers I
OL,8,Frepresent are incensed over this
OL,9,Fdecision. Following a successful
OL,10,FJudicial Review, the Federation
OL,11,Funanimously passed a vote of no
OL,12,Fconfidence in DCC Hamilton and the
OL,13,Fformer Chief Constable over their
OL,14,Fhandling of disciplinary issues around
OL,15,Fthe Ormeau Road incident in 2021.
