OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,F"In August 2023 a Judge found against
OL,8,Fthem and determined their actions to
OL,9,Fhave been unlawful. Mr Byrne
OL,10,Fultimately resigned and the newly
OL,11,Fappointed Chief Constable publicly
OL,12,Fapologised to the junior officers
OL,13,Finvolved.
OL,15,F"However, there has been no follow up
OL,16,Finvestigation instigated whatsoever
OL,17,Finto what actually occurred and,
OL,18,Ftherefore, no accountability for any
OL,19,Fof the decisions and punitive actions
OL,20,Ftaken by both senior officers against
OL,21,Ftheir junior colleagues.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G7/11
