OL,3,CPolice Federation hits out at
OL,4,Crecommendation to second senior PSNI
OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,F"The processes and system that
OL,8,Fseemingly allow such a two-tier
OL,9,Fapproach to disciplinary matters must
OL,10,Fbe challenged and ultimately
OL,11,Foverhauled. It has and continues to
OL,12,Ffail our rank-and-file officers who,
OL,13,Fit appears, are held to more stringent
OL,14,Foversight and a much higher standard
OL,15,Fthan their senior colleagues.
OL,17,F"If this recommendation is ratified by
OL,18,Fthe Justice Minister, my members will
OL,19,Fbe expecting a full explanation for
OL,20,Fthis decision.
