OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,F"The secondment request to the
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland Policing Board was
OL,9,Fbelatedly made by the Chief Constable
OL,10,Fafter both the Board and the Police
OL,11,FOmbudsman's Office clarified,
OL,12,Ffollowing legal advice they had
OL,13,Freceived, that there would be no
OL,14,Fcriminal or misconduct investigation
OL,15,Finto the matter.
