OL,3,CPolice Federation hits out at
OL,4,Crecommendation to second senior PSNI
OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,F"I have explained to Mr Boutcher the
OL,8,Finternal damage to rebuilding trust
OL,9,Fand confidence between the ranks that
OL,10,Fnews of this secondment will cause. We
OL,11,Fhave had members suspended and
OL,12,Frepositioned for years for matters
OL,13,Fthat are seemingly not as serious or
OL,14,Fdamaging to public confidence as this.
OL,16,F"There simply cannot be one rule for
OL,17,Fthose at senior levels in the PSNI and
OL,18,Fanother for the men and women I
OL,19,Frepresent."
